project:
YOU ARE A PACKER. YOUR LIFE DEPENDS ON BATTERY PACKS.

IN AN EFFORT TO CULL THE PACKER POPULATION, THE GOVERNMENT HAS STOPPED THE PRODUCTION OF BATTERY PACKS AND HAS SENT ITS TEAM OF DROIDS AND DROIDCARS TO ELIMINATE ALL PACKERS.

TO SURVIVE, YOU MUST ELIMINATE ENEMY DROIDS, DODGE DROIDCARS, AND COLLECT AS MANY BATTERY PACKS AS YOU CAN.

IF YOU FAIL TO KEEP YOUR CHARGE ABOVE ZERO, YOU WILL NOT SURVIVE.

IF YOU FAIL TO ELIMINATE GOVERNMENT DROIDS, YOU CANNOT PROCEED FURTHER INTO THE PACKER DISTRICT.

YOUR MISSION: PROCEED THROUGH THE THREE LEVELS OF THE PACKER DISTRICT, ELIMINATING GOVERNMENT DROIDS WHILE MAINTAINING YOUR CHARGE.

CONTROLS:


UP ARROW: JUMP/ DOUBLE-JUMP

DOWN ARROW: CROUCH

LEFT ARROW: MOVE LEFT

RIGHT ARROW: MOVE RIGHT

SPACE BAR: SHOOT

YOU HAVE SUCCESSFULLY SURVIVED THE GOVERNMENT'S PACKER ELIMINATION EFFORTS.


THANKS TO YOU, THE PACKER POPULATION WILL LIVE ON.


(UNTIL MORE DROIDS ARE SENT TO THE PACKER DISTRICT...)
